   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 1507, recto: (1) By this holy place (2) in which I am, in which my soul (3) is: As for the woman's dress (4) which I have received from you, (5) I gave you four tremisses (6) for it.  This is the oath (7) which Trempou (8) swore (9) to Trakote.  MH 1507, verso: (1) Aristophanes, son of John, (2) wrote.</ab>
